lou, Eudes 'Deco'|publisher=National Football Teams|accessdate=28 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%;\"\n! No !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 27 March 2018 || [[Stade de Marrakech]], [[Marrakesh]], [[Morocco]] || {{fb|KEN}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20132 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n*Champion of the [[Central African Republic League]] for 3 times in 2000, 2001, 2004 with [[Olympic Real de Bangui]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.scoresway.com/?sport=soccer&page=person&id=162351 Scoresway.com Profile]\n* [http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.eudes.dagoulou.118851.fr.html Eudes Dagoulou profile - ''footballdatabase'']\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dagoulou, Eudes}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Ombella-M'Poko]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Olympic Real de Bangui players]]\n[[Category:AS P\u00e9lican players]]\n[[Category:MC Oran players]]\n[[Category:ES S\u00e9tif players]]\n[[Category:Al-Wehda Club (Mecca) players]]\n[[Category:Burgan SC players]]\n[[Category:Gabon Championnat National D1 players]]\n[[Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 players]]\n[[Category:Saudi Professional League players]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic international footballers]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate sportspeople in Gabon]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate sportspeople in Algeria]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate sportspeople in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate sportspeople in Kuwait]]\n[[Category:Central African Republic expatriate sportspeople in Greece]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Gabon]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Algeria]]\